{
  "stem": "26576.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good afternoon.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name was Masha, M-A-S-H-A, Frydman, F-R-Y-D-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 22nd, of the 10th, 1927.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, about 69.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Sosnowiec, which was quite a big town on the-- so between-- very close to Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, what I remember-- Sosnowiec was a very sort-- a city where there was a lot of Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think there was 70,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a lot going on, like at one stage I was going even-- there were religious Jews, and there were non-religious Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I remember-- so like the house where we were living was quite a few very religious Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And although my father was really not a religious man, I had very high regard for him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was friendly with the religious Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also in the school where I was-- so it was-- the school was called [POLISH], which means that we were not a-- Saturday, we were not going to school, but Sunday, which was very unusual, because the Polish government at that stage was sort of half Fascist.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for to give allowances like that for Jewish kids was quite unusual.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was one of the schools that I was at.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I grew up with quite a good knowledge of Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had religious instructions and Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And those are the things so that one carries through life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Like my parents-- you want to know what my parents did and--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the name of my father was Josef Frydman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name of my mother was Yachet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They both came from a small town somewhere-- 100 kilometers from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The town was called Losice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father was a leader.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was a Bundist, and a leader in the trade union movement.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
